Uses of Class
Environment.Square

  • Packages that use Square 
    Package Description
    Environment  

    • Uses of Square in Environment

      Subclasses of Square in Environment 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BlankSquare
      Class Blank Square sets up a 'blank position' on the board where there are no objects (players, weapons etc) This is helpful for telling the game and board what is and what isn't at each coordinates of the board.
      class  Corridor
      The Corridor class is a square on the board which represents the corridor around the house.
      class  RoomSquare
      The room class extends square and represents a square in a room area of a board.
      Methods in Environment that return Square 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Square Board.getSquareAt(Position pos)
      Return a square on the board based on the given position.
